data.description: Welcome to 65 The Falls Blvd, where your dream of home sweet home begins. This delightful residence offers a unique blend of comfort, affordability, and versatility. Priced competitively, this property is ready to welcome a new family or savvy investor.  This 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home features LVP flooring throughout and tile bathroom floors. An added bonus to this already fantastic property is the heated and cooled bonus room that is waiting for you to add your own personal touch. Use it as a home office, playroom, or entertainment space - the choice is yours.  The spacious backyard provides the perfect canvas for gardening, playtime, or simply unwinding. Relax and take in the serene surroundings from the covered back porch – an ideal spot for morning coffee or evening gatherings.  There are NO HOA Rental Restrictions: Enjoy the freedom to maximize your investment potential. This home is perfect for investors or those seeking rental income opportunities. 65 The Falls Blvd is conveniently located, offering easy access to Covington's amenities, schools, and parks.   HVAC replaced in 2022 and roof replaced in 2014.  Don't miss out on the chance to make this house your home. Contact us today to schedule a showing and explore the potential of this property. Opportunities like this don't come around often, so act fast!
